Text.CultureInvariantString:
THAT LITTLE TWERP 
HUMGRUMP 
ZAPPED ME

AND VAPOURIZED ME INTO A 
CLOUD OF INK

ALL RATHER UNDIGNIFIED, 
I MUST SAY

IN MY CLOUDY FORM 
I FLOATED WISPILY 
THROUGH THE ROOM

UNTIL I FINALLY LANDED 
UPON A SHEET OF 
ULTRA ABSORBANT 
KITCHEN ROLL

AND THROUGH A 
LITTLE MAGIC, 
FOUND MYSELF... 
REFORMED
